{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"5b9054dc7f","title":"大字报诗——昔人已乘民主去","origin":"北京大学社会主义思想教育委员会编印《北京大学右派分子反动言论汇集》，一九五七年十月。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"254e69495f","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"5b9054dc7f"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"19f3f1b8ea","name":"北京大学"},{"id":"81d02828fd","name":"李燕生"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"20cf54b535","type":"title","text":"大字报诗——昔人已乘民主去","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5b9054dc7f"},{"id":"e5e625067c","type":"authors","text":"北京大学李燕生","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5b9054dc7f"},{"id":"ce14e22239","type":"subtitle","text":"（李燕生：北京大学化学系学生）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5b9054dc7f"},{"id":"061299c9ab","type":"subtitle","text":"诗三首","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5b9054dc7f"},{"id":"e0b93062b3","type":"subtitle","text":"一、昔人已乘民主去      李燕生","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5b9054dc7f"},{"id":"54698ce766","type":"paragraph","text":"近日燕园民主之风骤生。真理正义声不绝于耳。拙拈首，以抒昨日之情，以为应。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5b9054dc7f"},{"id":"20284bfa54","type":"paragraph","text":"昔人已乘民主去， (注一)","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5b9054dc7f"},{"id":"f8737562a4","type":"paragraph","text":"此地空余民主楼。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5b9054dc7f"},{"id":"d4399c2b45","type":"paragraph","text":"五四精精今安在，","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5b9054dc7f"},{"id":"74118c6379","type":"paragraph","text":"但风童颜尽白头。 (注二)","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5b9054dc7f"},{"id":"fe2ea4dcab","type":"paragraph","text":"得意扬扬官易作，","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5b9054dc7f"},{"id":"ab8346c418","type":"paragraph","text":"平庸碌碌学难求。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5b9054dc7f"},{"id":"64cf629208","type":"paragraph","text":"唯唯诺诺何处是，","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5b9054dc7f"},{"id":"da06fc0afe","type":"paragraph","text":"未名湖畔使人愁。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5b9054dc7f"},{"id":"96a353dd25","type":"paragraph","text":"注一；昔人指争民主争自由之烈士，非反动派也。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5b9054dc7f"},{"id":"e019806df8","type":"paragraph","text":"注二；尽白头系少年老成之意，不是变了白毛女式的白毛男，特此声明，“批抨”家雅量。","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5b9054dc7f"},{"id":"8e490c7e95","type":"subtitle","text":"二、整风插曲      李燕生","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5b9054dc7f"},{"id":"f5b268f0a8","type":"paragraph","text":"你从前是这样","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5b9054dc7f"},{"id":"6efde73557","type":"paragraph","text":"现在还是这样","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5b9054dc7f"},{"id":"75155f8221","type":"paragraph","text":"官僚的你","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5b9054dc7f"},{"id":"d43f4407c5","type":"paragraph","text":"勇敢的熊","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5b9054dc7f"},{"id":"d43e7d1c47","type":"paragraph","text":"你为什么","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5b9054dc7f"},{"id":"d2748e4a6e","type":"paragraph","text":"为什么如此沉静","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5b9054dc7f"},{"id":"f5b993a6a4","type":"paragraph","text":"难道你以为是一阵风","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5b9054dc7f"},{"id":"921389ca21","type":"subtitle","text":"三、上当了——给三害大人      李燕生","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5b9054dc7f"},{"id":"788fe45ff0","type":"paragraph","text":"连日响应鸣放，","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5b9054dc7f"},{"id":"ada8310327","type":"paragraph","text":"今日始知上当，","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5b9054dc7f"},{"id":"3aae691a4e","type":"paragraph","text":"实在怪多太混帐，","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5b9054dc7f"},{"id":"f13579af07","type":"paragraph","text":"三害大人原谅。","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5b9054dc7f"},{"id":"6bb3b348bc","type":"paragraph","text":"整风，整风，","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5b9054dc7f"},{"id":"e2e910649a","type":"paragraph","text":"争鸣，争鸣，","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5b9054dc7f"},{"id":"fb52b9f8f8","type":"paragraph","text":"我年幼无知，","index":31,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5b9054dc7f"},{"id":"90cecd6df9","type":"paragraph","text":"经验不灵，","index":32,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5b9054dc7f"},{"id":"c6874ffe2a","type":"paragraph","text":"把心里想的，","index":33,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5b9054dc7f"},{"id":"ee5b5887f0","type":"paragraph","text":"一起说清","index":34,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5b9054dc7f"},{"id":"33aa2d294a","type":"paragraph","text":"得到的不是说理，","index":35,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5b9054dc7f"},{"id":"23e2324f5c","type":"paragraph","text":"而是围攻。","index":36,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5b9054dc7f"},{"id":"f71661f05c","type":"paragraph","text":"说我是","index":37,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5b9054dc7f"},{"id":"fb6a121a32","type":"paragraph","text":"杜勒斯的传声筒；","index":38,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5b9054dc7f"},{"id":"0b06e3a2f7","type":"paragraph","text":"说我是","index":39,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5b9054dc7f"},{"id":"f8fbe8b574","type":"paragraph","text":"什么“自由之声”。","index":40,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5b9054dc7f"},{"id":"d8f4f892b9","type":"paragraph","text":"它叫我细雨和风，","index":41,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5b9054dc7f"},{"id":"b6b7b15df3","type":"paragraph","text":"他对我闪电雷轰。","index":42,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5b9054dc7f"},{"id":"97267e0e39","type":"paragraph","text":"一切本人皆看清，","index":43,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5b9054dc7f"},{"id":"31e99e26e4","type":"paragraph","text":"从明天起埋头书本；","index":44,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5b9054dc7f"},{"id":"a5e55405de","type":"paragraph","text":"乘乘风凉，","index":45,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5b9054dc7f"},{"id":"1ce36ee5a1","type":"paragraph","text":"悠然度余生。","index":46,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5b9054dc7f"}],"page":{"id":"8aafddf09b","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5b9054dc7f","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}